            section(id="about")
                .bio
                    h2 Bio
                    p Based out of Austin, Texas I specialize in javascript driven websites. This includes data visualization, web cartgography, and web applications. 
                    p My background is in marketing and GIS so I am constantly thinking on how we can use the web to solve business problems spatially.
                .skills
                    h2 Skills
                    p I spend most of my time in Javascript and SASS. I have experience scripting with python, mainly for data sanitization and data scrapping. Libraries I use regularly are Leaflet, JQuery, Kartography, and I am currently experiementing with Angular.
                    p Most importantly I am empathetic to the needs of clients and the importance of providing timely and stable solutions. I have experience working in an agile system; individually and with teams.  
                .cred
                    h2 Cred
                    p I am a graduate of University of Texas's School of Advertising. While at UT I was a productions intern for an advertising firm.  
                    p Recently I have worked with a Crisis PR firm handling their digital response - website, social media, emails - for clients ranging from law firms to city governments.


